videos.headline: Pittsburgh RB breaks free for 69-yard TD
videos.description: Pittsburgh gets on the board as Qadree Ollison eludes defenders for a 69-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Pittsburgh takes fumble for 35-yard TD
videos.description: Pittsburgh defense comes up big as it forces a fumble that is recovered by Dane Jackson, who takes it 35 yards for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Pittsburgh's Araujo-Lopes takes catch 68-yards for TD
videos.description: Kenny Pickett finds Rafael Araujo-Lopes as he avoids Syracuse defenders for a 68-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Syracuse QB dives for TD
videos.description: Eric Dungey escapes the pocket to run in a 21-yard touchdown for Syracuse.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-play (Syracuse QB dives over pineline for TD) 2018/10/06

videos.headline: Pittsburgh RB rushes in go-ahead TD in OT
videos.description: Pittsburgh's Darren Hall runs in a go-ahead 1-yard touchdown in overtime against Syracuse.
